.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, spanish, argentine, german, brazilian, british, turkish
 1. the german is not to the left of the british##8
 2. the turkish is in an even position##4
 3. the british is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
 4. the brazilian is on the left or right of the british##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the british##3
 6. the turkish is not to the right of the russian##8
 7. the argentine is somewhere between the british and the spanish##7
 8. the russian is in an odd position##4
 9. the russian is not to the right of the argentine##8
10. the british is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | german | turkish | russian | argentine | spanish |

