.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, october, december, february, may, april, september
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in february##7
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in september##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Birthday   | december | june | february | september | may | october | april |

