5. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
9. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Transport   | taxi | quad-bike | trike | jet-ski | helicopter | scooter | subway |

